\s Utukufu wa Mbinguni ni wa heri 
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Utukufu wa \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd  ni wa heri na amani, dhambi hazitakuwamo. Vitu vyote vilivyomo ni vya tunu na thamani, dhambi hazitakuwamo. \bd*
\pc \bdit Dhambi hazitaingia \bdit*\bdit Mbingu\bdit*\bdit  ya utakatifu. Ukidumu mwenye dhambi bila kutakaswa huku, hutaingia \bdit*\bdit Mbingu\bdit*\bdit ni\bdit*\bdit . \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Kama unatumaini kufikia nchi ile na kuona Bwana \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd , utafute utakaso na kupata moyo safi! Dhambi hazitakuwamo. \bd*
\pc \bdit Dhambi hazitaingia \bdit*\bdit Mbingu\bdit*\bdit  ya utakatifu. Ukidumu mwenye dhambi bila kutakaswa huku, hutaingia \bdit*\bdit Mbingu\bdit*\bdit ni\bdit*\bdit . \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Unaweza ’tenda dhambi na kukana Bwana \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd , walakini ukumbuke: Dhambi zako zitafunga lango la \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd , kwani dhambi hazitakuwamo. \bd*
\pc \bdit Dhambi hazitaingia \bdit*\bdit Mbingu\bdit*\bdit  ya utakatifu. Ukidumu mwenye dhambi bila kutakaswa huku, hutaingia \bdit*\bdit Mbingu\bdit*\bdit ni\bdit*\bdit . \bdit*
