\pc \bdit Ukitaka kufikako \bdit*\bdit Mbingu\bdit*\bdit  ya utakatifu, tubu sasa, hacha dhambi, utafute moyo safi, na utaingia \bdit*\bdit Mbingu\bdit*\bdit ! \bdit*
